reviewText: When I made recent order, Amazon product description/photo showed CFR Getting Together as 5 DVD discs including the main program (4DVD discs) and separately boxed "Backstage" 1DVD disc for price of US$79.80.  Received main program 4 DVD's without "Backstage" separately box/disc. I am very dissapointed, as I wanted & paid for the complete 5DVD disc program. Amazon advised "Inventory" problem & cannot supply "Backstage" 1DVD disc.  Amazon continues to advertise/product description as 5DVD discs set. This is occurring whenever the CFR set of 5DVD discs product including the separately boxed "Backstage" 1DVD is ordered.  Refer attached photo.
Excellent dvd great price fast ship
A GREAT ADDITION TO THE FAMILY REUNION SERIES HOSTED BY BILL ANDERSON. SEE STARS PAST AND PRESENT PERFORM THEIR GREATEST HITS IN A ONE OF A KIND SHOW.
